# Styling & Tailwind Patterns

## Color Palette
```javascript
// From index.html tailwind.config
colors: {
  primary: '#1a1a1a',      // Dark/Black - text, backgrounds
  secondary: '#8c2438',    // Wine Red - CTAs, accents, brand
  accent: '#d4af37',       // Gold - luxury highlights
}
```

## Typography
```tsx
// Font family
className="font-sans"    // Noto Sans Hebrew (body)
className="Noto Sans Hebrew"   // Headings, brand

// Sizes
className="text-xs"      // 12px - labels, badges
className="text-sm"      // 14px - body small
className="text-base"    // 16px - body
className="text-lg"      // 18px - subheadings
className="text-xl"      // 20px
className="text-2xl"     // 24px
className="text-3xl"     // 30px - section titles
className="text-4xl"     // 36px - page titles
className="text-6xl"     // 60px - hero

// Weight
className="font-medium"  // 500
className="font-bold"    // 700
```

## Button Patterns

### Primary CTA (Wine Red)
```tsx
className="bg-secondary hover:bg-red-900 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-bold transition-colors shadow-md hover:shadow-xl"
```

### Outline Button
```tsx
className="border-2 border-gray-900 text-gray-900 px-10 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-gray-900 hover:text-white transition-colors"
```

### Icon Button
```tsx
className="p-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-secondary transition-colors"
```

### Hero CTA (White/Light)
```tsx
className="group flex items-center gap-4 bg-white text-black px-12 py-5 rounded-full font-bold text-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(255,255,255,0.2)]"
```

## Card Patterns

### Product Card
```tsx
className="group relative bg-white border border-transparent hover:border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"
```

### Info Card
```tsx
className="p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded border border-gray-100"
```

### Feature Card
```tsx
className="flex flex-col items-center p-4"
```

## Layout Patterns

### Container
```tsx
className="container mx-auto px-4"
```

### Fixed Header
```tsx
className="fixed top-0 w-full bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md shadow-sm z-40 border-b border-gray-100"
```

### Modal Overlay
```tsx
// Backdrop
className="fixed inset-0 z-50"
className="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-sm"

// Panel
className="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full max-w-md h-full bg-white shadow-2xl"
```

### Grid Layouts
```tsx
// Product grid
className="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6"
className="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8"

// Features grid
className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8"
```

## Image Patterns

### Product Image Container
```tsx
className="relative aspect-[2/3] overflow-hidden bg-gray-50"
// or
className="aspect-[3/4] bg-gray-50 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"
```

### Image with Hover Scale
```tsx
className="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
```

## Badge Patterns

### Sale Badge
```tsx
className="absolute top-3 end-3 bg-red-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded"
```

### Cart Count Badge
```tsx
className="absolute top-0 -end-1 bg-secondary text-white text-[10px] w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-bold"
```

## Loading States

### Skeleton
```tsx
className="h-96 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg animate-pulse"
```

### Loading Text
```tsx
<div className="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">טוען...</div>
```

## Hover Effects

### Card Overlay
```tsx
className="absolute inset-0 bg-black/10 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
```

### Button Transform
```tsx
className="transform translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 duration-300"
className="transform hover:-translate-y-1"
```

## Spacing Conventions
```tsx
// Sections
className="py-20"        // Large section padding
className="py-10"        // Medium section padding
className="mb-16"        // Section title margin

// Components
className="p-6"          // Card padding
className="gap-4"        // Item spacing
className="space-y-4"    // Vertical stack
```

